President Muhammadu Buhari met with the General Overseer of the Latter Rain Assembly (LRA), Pastor Tunde Bakare, yesterday at the Presidential Villa. The visit may be connected to President Buhari’s victory at the just concluded presidential polls. Recall that Pastor Bakare was  president Buhari’s  running mate on the platform of Congress for Progressive Change( CPC) in the 2011 presidential elections. Pastor Bakare did not speak to State House correspondents after meeting with the president.